Install Vscode 
https://code.visualstudio.com/download
Install Docker
https://docs.docker.com/desktop/setup/install/windows-install/

Go to vsccode cretae new projet

create a new file .env and add the following lines:

AIRFLOW_IMAGE_NAME=apache/airflow:2.4.2
AIRFLOW_UID=50000

save docker-compose.yaml file: https://github.com/idiattara/Airflow_THIES_SORBONE/blob/main/docker-compose.yaml  in your project
run the flowing commande
docker-compose up -d

docker-compose up airflow-init

docker-compose run --rm airflow-webserver airflow db init


create Admin user using below command:
 Mot de passe par defaut :  airflow airflow
docker-compose run airflow-worker airflow users create --role Admin --username admin --email admin --firstname admin --lastname admin --password admin


















